<h2 id="blog-post-card">Blog post card</h2>

<p>Add an image to your blog post card to make it eye-catching. You can do it by adding the image in the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.card-img-top</code> class. Thanks to the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.d-flex</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.flex-column</code> classes within <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.card-body</code>, the author details will be displayed at the bottom of the card.</p>

<div class="example no_toc_section example-bg">
