<h2 id="color-variations">Color variations</h2>

<p>Add a status color to your card, either at the top or on the side of the card, to customise it and make it more eye-catching.</p>

<div class="example no_toc_section example-bg">
	<div class="example-content">
		
		<div class="example-column example-column-2">
		
		

		
<div class="row row-deck">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
			<div class="card-status-top bg-danger"></div>
		<div class="card-body">
			<h3 class="card-title">Card with top status</h3>
			<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Aperiam deleniti fugit incidunt, iste, itaque minima
				neque pariatur perferendis sed suscipit velit vitae voluptatem.</p>
		</div>
</div>

    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
			<div class="card-status-start bg-green"></div>
		<div class="card-body">
			<h3 class="card-title">Card with side status</h3>
			<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Aperiam deleniti fugit incidunt, iste, itaque minima
				neque pariatur perferendis sed suscipit velit vitae voluptatem.</p>
		</div>
</div>

    </div>
</div>


		
		</div>
		
	</div>
</div>

